Interface Joiner2Factory

public interface Joiner2Factory

Factory to construct instances of Joiner2. Unless an additional layer of indirection is required for mocking or testing, it is usually sufficient to call Joiner2Utils.withSeparator(String).

Author:
Kevin Connor ARPE (kevinarpe@gmail.com)
